{{Timeline of the Galactic Civil War/LightCell|bg=FF9966|page=Assault on Yavin 4|ref=<ref name="Darksaber" /> (47:7)<ref name="Months">The [[Battle of Nam Chorios]] occurs in [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]], while the [[Battle of Orinda]] occurs in [[12 ABY/Legends|12 ABY]]. According to the ''Essential Chronology'' and the ''New Essential Chronology'', Nam Chorios occurs a month after Orinda. The only way for Orinda to occur in 12 ABY and Nam Chorios in 13 ABY is if Nam Chorios was within a month of the division between the two years, or 48:3. This means that Orinda must occur in 48:2, a month earlier. Also, the [[Orinda campaign]] lasts a month, meaning that the [[raid on Orinda]] occurred in 48:1. Similarly, the [[Assault on Yavin 4]] happens in 47:7, as both Chronologies state that Pellaeon starts the Orinda campaign six months after Daala's defeat and resignation.</ref>|combatants=[[File:NR_Seal.svg|18px|link=New Republic/Legends]] [[File:New_Jedi_Order.svg|18px|link=New Jedi Order]] v. [[File:Imperial_Emblem.svg|18px|link=Imperial Remnant]]}}
